3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5InXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=9762aadd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35JC1av.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35JC1av.jpg&h=abb74f02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"880f796bb63887741fbe001df8afa54d8852249c","tid":1855430,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T11:20:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be071a6b66e4518d379ae5eebd824231b0436a9a","tid":1855430,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:23:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好撚多人香港開工番大陸住.日日來回<br />\n不如借呢次cut走埋呢班假香港人</span>"},{"pid":"0cb2e6ec98c47e6db549a97db95c72a31a2c0ab1","tid":1855430,"uid":322412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T16:28:41.000Z","msg":"📢民主黨發起全港簽名運動<br />\n支持醫護 封關救港 禁止內地人來港<br />\n<br />\n✅ 網上聯署連結: shorturl.at/iHSVZ<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎襲港，內地確診個案已經突破一萬大關，全中國擴散，香港亦已經超過14個確診個案。封關是阻止疫情擴散的重中之重的必須手段。<br />\n<br />\n內地患者源源不絕來港求醫，醫療系統無可能應付全國需求。林鄭拒封關，醫護系統爆煲，香港人人自危。醫護人員發動罷工要求封關，是保護港人下迫於無奈的一步。<br />\n<br />\n因此，我們要求政府：<br />\n<br />\n1. 支持醫護人員訴求，即時封關，於關口採取嚴厲管制入境措施，禁止內地人來港；及<br />\n<br />\n2. 提供足夠口罩及防護裝備給醫護人員，前線公務員及市民，並制訂措施禁止商人抬價。<br />\n#民主黨 #撐醫護 #罷工 #封關 #聯署 #林卓延<br />\n0<br />\n0"},{"pid":"9fb3975f01900fdd33f2b9e7187bdc6bcc10b8c5","tid":1855430,"uid":322412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:00:47.000Z","msg":"罷工人數調查<br />\nPWH <br />\n7A ~7<br />\n7B ~17<br />\n10C ~10 +10ccu 8<br />\n11A ~17<br />\n11C ～16<br />\n12B ~ 14<br />\n10LM ~20<br />\nNNU: 73<br />\n11HKLM: 23<br />\n4Eonco:~7<br />\nCIC~5<br />\n<br />\nPrivate: ~17<br />\n<br />\nolmh E3：～10<br />\n<br />\nUch <br />\n10B: ~12<br />\n12B: ~14<br />\nUCH Physio: 40<br />\n<br />\nPY ICU: ~33<br />\n<br />\nYCH<br />\